      "widgets_values": [
        "\u2139\ufe0f Luminosity Masking (S-05)\n\nDefaults: luminance_source=lab_l, shadow_end=0.33, highlight_start=0.67, soft_edge=0.1.\n\n- luminance_source: 'lab_l' perceptual (~120ms @ 2K CPU, Photoshop default); 'ycbcr_y' fast path (~7ms @ 1024 CPU); 'hsv_v' simple max-RGB.\n- 3 outputs are smooth MASK pins: shadows / midtones / highlights.\n- Partition of unity: shadows + midtones + highlights \u2248 1.0 per pixel.\n- Use for local contrast, color grading, dodge/burn by luminance band.\n- Pairs with MaskCompose / ImageBlend to combine grading layers.\n- shadow_end must be < highlight_start (node raises otherwise)."
      ],
